{"tid":2246936,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Mario Kart Live 來貨少炒價達 HK$1,100　香港有商場收 $50 玩一局","createTime":"2020-10-17T12:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T08:53:34.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"059413f274f71ee07f3596c0abc29bde1039242e","tid":2246936,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"任天堂近日將推出一款《Mario Kart Live: Home Circuit》配合遊戲機與遙控車的賽車遊戲，不過這款遊戲由於貨源缺乏，原價港幣約 HK$730 的遊戲在網路上被炒至 HK$1,100。香港最近就有一家室內遊戲中心以 Mario Kart Live 作招徠，以圖吸引消費者光顧，不過就要在商場累積消費滿一定金額，或直接支付 HK$50 才可玩一回合。<br />\n<br />\n香港一家室內遊戲中心近日以 Mario Kart Live 作招徠，指遊戲中心會員只要於指定商場及商戶內累積消費滿一定金額，即可免費體驗&nbsp;Mario Kart Live: Home Circuit 一次，而非會員則要支付入場費 HK$50 才可試玩。不過該商場宣傳活動並無標明同香港任天堂合作，而且更強行將 Mario 的眼睛除去，有違反著作權以及利用遊戲軟件作營利用途之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2020-10-16_17_30_54-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596_2020-10-16_17_30_54-1.jpg&h=00d01619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMario Kart Live: Home Circuit&nbsp;乃是任天堂 Switch 剛推出的一款遊戲，玩家可以透過實體的遙控車與攝影鏡頭，在主機上以 AR 的方式以「現實世界」作賽道遊玩&nbsp;Mario Kart，現時官方售價約為&nbsp;HKD$730。"},{"pid":"502e00bbe25ebf80d24769ac421991a7d4fce6e3","tid":2246936,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"$720 &gt; $1100<br />\n<br />\n升50%<br />\n好過炒股<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2169d027d5ca4b602f7da77943b98cd5179be5cc","tid":2246936,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"598c3d57d0b712897e679c5c98d4bc0ddae7e165","tid":2246936,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:17:50.000Z",